Package: tinyqueue
Type: Package
Title: A Simple Task Queue
Version: 0.0.1
Date: 2025-07-04
Authors@R: person("Dirk", "Eddelbuettel", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "edd@debian.org")
Description: A task queue is provided with simple operator modeled after existing
 task queue functionality. By relying on either Redis or Valkey as a backend,
 a suitable degree of concurrency of worker nodes is provided.
Imports: methods, RcppRedis
URL: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/tinyqueue
BugReports: https://github.com/eddelbuettel/tinyqueue/issues
